description.en:
CircleEx aims to empower cryptocurrency users to make informed decisions when it comes to buying and selling their assets. Our platform will also enrich the user experience by offering stupendous value when it comes to liquidity on the platform. 

Apart from facilitating the best possible exchange values to the users, CircleEx will be permitting its users to partake in governance decisions and add more value to the wider community. Using our CX tokens, the users will have the freedom to use the platform at its superior capacity.
